      "title": "Alaric<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\"></div>",
      "html": "<p>西哥特人的男性名字，字面意思是“全能的统治者”，源自原始日耳曼语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">*ala-</i> “全部”（见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of all \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/all\">all</a>）+ <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">*rikja</i> “统治”（来自 PIE 词根 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *reg- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/*reg-\">*reg-</a> “沿直线移动”，具有“沿直线引导”的派生词义，因此意为“领导，统治”）。</p>"
